title: 820-3476-a turn on no display
message:
Unit had water damaged close to R5498 and C5549.
R5494 : 17.75v. Fan spinning normal,  CPU is not getting worm.
 Missing EDP_PANEL_PWR_OR_PSR_EN on pin 1 R8319
Have PP3V3_S0 on pin 8 of U8330 .
PP5VS4 is present.
PPVCC_S0_CPU: 1.69V
Known good display connected.
Dont know what to next, any help please.

title: 820-3476-a turn on no display
message:
Pins 28-30 of J8300 must get 5V, at least in the first few seconds.
This voltage is not maintained if pins 1 & 4 of U8330 don't go high.
Checl these pins and be sure L8300 is OK.

title: 820-3476-a turn on no display
message:
Pins 28-30 of J8300=0v

1 & 4 of U8330: 0v
L8300 is OK.

Disconnect J8300 and test again.
